If &lt;code&gt;this.state.name&lt;/code&gt; is a &lt;code&gt;String&lt;/code&gt; containing multiple names with new line (&lt;code&gt;\n&lt;/code&gt;) delimiters in it, then you can first extract an array of names from the string and then use the above code, for example:

